title: NASA's studying how zero gravity affects the brain
text:
NASA's studying how zero gravity affects the brain 
Published By: Tuaw.com - Today 
Because there's no up or down in zero gravity, the way our brains calculate 3D space stops working. As it turns out, that can be problematic...
